---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="How Payments Tech Helps Freight Forwarders | Case Study"
  description="Discover how JBM Freight uses new technologies to power its growth as an independent freight forwarder and to free time to service its customers better."
>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="mb-8 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Case Studies</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-text-heading font-medium">JBM Freight</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Tags -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-green-pale text-brand-green text-[0.8125rem] font-semibold rounded-full">
          Logistics
        </span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-text-muted text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-full">
          Digitalisation
        </span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-text-muted text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-full">
          Cash Management
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-text-heading leading-tight mb-4">
        How the right payment technology helped launch logistics at the peak of the pandemic
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[1.25rem] text-brand-green font-semibold mb-10">JBM Freight</p>

      <!-- Pull Quote -->
      <blockquote class="my-10 p-8 bg-brand-green-pale rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-green">
        <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-text-heading leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;Being able to pull the invoices and just pay them directly with HedgeFlows is great. It's not a challenge anymore. Feeding invoices back to Xero — I didn't know that was even a challenge and now you guys do it for me!&rdquo;
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-4">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Alice-JBM-Freight.jpg?width=96&name=Alice-JBM-Freight.jpg" alt="Alice, co-founder of JBM Freight" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          <cite class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body not-italic font-medium">
            &mdash; Alice, Co-founder
          </cite>
        </div>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Content Sections -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE COMPANY</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Customers at the heart of everything
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>JBM Freight is a Manchester-based freight forwarder that opened its doors at the peak of the pandemic, in early 2020.</p>
<p>The founders Ben and Alice have a strong vision — to provide customers with great service and leverage technology to make it efficient. They aim one day to become the biggest non-asset freight-forwarder in the UK.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE PROBLEM</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Building a business during a pandemic
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>JBM launched a business at the start of a pandemic, but were also hit with the impacts of Brexit, price increases for sea freight and containers, driver shortages and currency volatility. It's been an enlightening journey, and they've had to learn quickly.</p>
<p>Expensive desktop-based software solutions, that their larger competitors can rely on, were out of reach for JBM when they started.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE SOLUTION</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          The right technology
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>JBM's smart technology choices are what helped them deliver on their vision. They used a government grant to invest in a freight software solution initially and then turned to cloud-based software where they could — Xero for their accounting and HedgeFlows for payments.</p>
<p>Cloud-based software such as HedgeFlows and Xero integrate well and give the team the most up-to-date information across systems. Having it all integrated and easy to use has been transformative for their operations.</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Ratesmove.png?width=500&name=Ratesmove.png" alt="HedgeFlows rates movement tracking" class="mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-sm max-w-[280px]" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="mt-2 text-[0.8125rem] text-text-muted text-center">Real-time rate tracking in HedgeFlows</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE IMPACT</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Saving time and money to do what matters
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p><strong>Saving time</strong> &mdash; The HedgeFlows technology is easy to read, transparent, and explains what it's going to do. Being able to pull invoices and pay them directly, with automatic reconciliation back to Xero, has removed manual challenges entirely.</p>
<p><strong>Building relationships with customers</strong> &mdash; Alice is clear about how she spends the time that the team saves thanks to this technology — to meet and get to know more customers. Being more proactive, going out to see customers and asking them what they need.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="my-8 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-[1rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;Having it all — integrated, easy to use. It's just been a dream. Really. The HedgeFlows tech is easy to read. It's transparent. It explains what it's going to do.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-3 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted not-italic font-medium">
          &mdash; Alice, Co-founder
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-green font-semibold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
          Back to case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    headline="Want similar results for your business?"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Book a Treasury Review', href: '/treasury-health-check' }}
  />
</PageLayout>
